However, what takes the MH12 to the next level is its integrated micro-USB charging port, making life much easier when its time to charge it back up. Measuring in at 5.47 inch and weighing just over three ounces, the MH12 just may be the perfect, portable, and lightweight EDC flashlight out today. The MH12 produces a blistering 1000 Lumens, with a maximum throw of 232 meters, which is accessed via the intuitive two-button user interface. Combine that with its three special modes, Strobe, SOS, and Location Beacon, the MH12 is the perfect light for the everyday user, law enforcement, campers, and adventurers.Nitecore MH12 Flashlight Black
